<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RapNation Visitor Guide</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="theme-dark">

    <%- include("../partials/navbar") %>

    <header class="page-hero page-hero-advice">
        <div class="page-hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="container page-hero-content">
            <p class="section-kicker">Visitor Guide</p>
            <h1>Festival Advice & Help</h1>
            <p>
                Everything you need to know before the event, from online viewing
                to support tips and festival-day guidance.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="section section-dark">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-heading">
                    <p class="section-kicker">Plan Ahead</p>
                    <h2>Useful Information Before You Arrive</h2>
                    <p>
                        Get prepared so you can enjoy the RapNation experience without missing a moment.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="guide-grid">
                    <article class="guide-card">
                        <div class="guide-icon">01</div>
                        <h3>Watch Online</h3>
                        <p>
                            If you cannot make it to the event in person, you can follow select moments online
                            and stay updated through the livestream experience.
                        </p>
                        <a href="https://zoom.us/download" class="btn btn-secondary">Download Zoom</a>
                    </article>

                    <article class="guide-card">
                        <div class="guide-icon">02</div>
                        <h3>Ticket Support</h3>
                        <p>
                            Double-check your ticket details early and contact support ahead of time if anything
                            looks incorrect or needs clarification.
                        </p>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Help</a>
                    </article>

                    <article class="guide-card">
                        <div class="guide-icon">03</div>
                        <h3>Plan Your Schedule</h3>
                        <p>
                            Review the lineup and stages before the festival so you know where to go for the
                            biggest performances and special moments.
                        </p>
                        <a href="/stages" class="btn btn-secondary">See Stages</a>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section section-surface">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-heading">
                    <p class="section-kicker">Common Questions</p>
                    <h2>Quick Answers</h2>
                    <p>Helpful details for a smoother festival experience.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-list">
                    <article class="faq-card">
                        <h3>What should I do if I cannot attend in person?</h3>
                        <p>
                            Use the livestream or online access options to stay connected with key parts of the event.
                            We recommend installing Zoom in advance if remote viewing is needed.
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <article class="faq-card">
                        <h3>Where can I get help with tickets or event questions?</h3>
                        <p>
                            Visit the contact page to send your questions directly. You can also check comments
                            from other visitors for extra guidance and shared feedback.
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <article class="faq-card">
                        <h3>How do I make sure I don’t miss the main performances?</h3>
                        <p>
                            Review the lineup and stage schedule before the festival begins. Planning ahead helps
                            you move between zones more easily and catch the biggest acts.
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <article class="faq-card">
                        <h3>What is the best way to prepare for the festival day?</h3>
                        <p>
                            Confirm your ticket details, check the schedule, decide which stages matter most to you,
                            and arrive early enough to enjoy the full atmosphere.
                        </p>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section section-dark">
            <div class="container cta-banner">
                <div>
                    <p class="section-kicker">Need More Help?</p>
                    <h2>Get Support or Join the Conversation</h2>
                    <p>
                        Reach out directly or see what other people are saying about the RapNation experience.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="cta-actions">
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
                    <a href="/comments" class="btn btn-secondary">View Comments</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include("../partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>